<html><head><title>Britain In Brief</title></head><body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<center><p align=center>
<table width=65% align=center><tr><td valign=top align=center>
<img src="http://www.economist.com/econlogosmall.gif" width="78" height="39" alt="The Economist" border=0>
