<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/23-11-96/wb8465.html 199.173.162.110 19970113141021 text/html 11383
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:06:36 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 21-Nov-96 18:54:10 GMT
