<DOCNO>WT21-B38-19</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000273-B042-203</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/16-11-96/am3126.html 199.173.162.110 19970113141255 text/html 9844
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:09:07 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 14-Nov-96 18:26:46 GMT
Content-length: 9659
