<DOCNO>WT21-B38-28</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000273-B043-17</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/16-11-96/wb8443.html 199.173.162.110 19970113141725 text/html 11326
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:13:31 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 14-Nov-96 19:00:13 GMT
Content-length: 11140
