<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/09-11-96/am3116.html 199.173.162.110 19970113142031 text/html 7101
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:16:43 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 07-Nov-96 18:11:27 GMT
Content-length: 6916
