<DOCNO>WT21-B38-40</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000273-B044-11</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/09-11-96/am3117.html 199.173.162.110 19970113142137 text/html 6526
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:17:28 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 07-Nov-96 17:45:17 GMT
Content-length: 6341
