http://www.economist.com:80/issue/09-11-96/br7578.html 199.173.162.110 19970113142537 text/html 7295
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:21:52 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 07-Nov-96 17:45:18 GMT
Content-length: 7110
