<DOCNO>WT21-B38-74</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000273-B046-247</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/02-11-96/fn6444.html 199.173.162.110 19970113143300 text/html 8429
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
