http://www.economist.com:80/issue/19-10-96/bw0756.html 199.173.162.110 19970113144014 text/html 6731
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:36:30 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 17-Oct-96 16:04:11 GMT
