<DOCNO>WT21-B38-95</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000273-B048-144</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/19-10-96/sf0774.html 199.173.162.110 19970113144038 text/html 17366
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:36:50 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 17-Oct-96 17:34:13 GMT
