<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/05-10-96/ir5980.html 199.173.162.110 19970113145254 text/html 5846
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:49:10 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 03-Oct-96 19:49:31 GMT
