<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/05-10-96/st4052.html 199.173.162.110 19970113145519 text/html 8757
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 14:51:33 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 03-Oct-96 19:49:31 GMT
