<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/issue/31-08-96/wb2.html 199.173.162.110 19970113152619 text/html 7911
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 15:22:32 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 29-Aug-96 18:02:02 GMT
