http://www.economist.com:80/issue/10-08-96/fn1.html 199.173.162.110 19970113154418 text/html 3617
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 15:40:33 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 18:10:21 GMT
