http://www.economist.com:80/issue/27-07-96/sf1.html 199.173.162.110 19970113155337 text/html 20996
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 15:49:45 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 14:14:54 GMT
